6.9.\n* Fix - Resolved an issue where the Course and Group fields would not show properly when editing an Event.\n* Tweak - Updated required PHP version to 7.4.\n* Tweak - Updated required WP version to 6.6.\";s:4:\"name\";s:37:\"LearnDash Events Calendar Integration\";s:11:\"description\";s:182:\"The Events Calendar (TEC) is the most popular Events platform for WordPress. This integration allows you to connect an event with a course or group and automatically enroll the user.\";s:8:\"category\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"authors\";a:1:{i:0;s:9:\"LearnDash\";}s:17:\"documentation_url\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:59:\"https://www.learndash.com/integrations/the-events-calendar/\";s:11:\"plugin_file\";s:24:\"ld-tec/learndash-tec.php\";}i:10;a:16:{s:4:\"slug\";s:16:\"learndash-zapier\";s:4:\"kind\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:12:\"minimum_tier\";s:10:\"essentials\";s:7:\"top_dir\";s:16:\"learndash-zapier\";s:9:\"main_file\";s:20:\"learndash_zapier.php\";s:10:\"wporg_slug\";N;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"2.3.2\";s:12:\"release_date\";s:10:\"2026-01-21\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:345:\"* Tweak - LearnDash requirement has been updated to 4.6.0.\n* Tweak - Updated required PHP version to 7.4.\n* Tweak - Updated required WP version to 6.6.\n* Tweak - Added actions: `learndash_zapier_uninstall`.\n* Tweak - Deprecated classes: `LearnDash_Dependency_Check_LD_Zapier`.\n* Tweak - Deprecated functions: `learndash_zapier_check_dependency`.\";s:4:\"name\";s:28:\"LearnDash Zapier Integration\";s:11:\"description\";s:276:\"Zapier is a service that makes it easy for you to connect two applications without the need to know code, currently with a library of over 300 applications. Zapier calls these connections ÔÇ£ZapsÔÇØ, and this integration lets you create Zaps that include LearnDash activities.\";s:8:\"category\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"authors\";a:1:{i:0;s:9:\"LearnDash\";}s:17:\"documentation_url\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:58:\"https://www.learndash.com/integrations/zapier-integration/\";s:11:\"plugin_file\";s:37:\"learndash-zapier/learndash_zapier.php\";}i:11;a:16:{s:4:\"slug\";s:25:\"learndash-paidmemberships\";s:4:\"kind\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:12:\"minimum_tier\";s:10:\"essentials\";s:7:\"top_dir\";s:25:\"learndash-paidmemberships\";s:9:\"main_file\";s:29:\"learndash-paidmemberships.php\";s:10:\"wporg_slug\";N;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.3.5\";s:12:\"release_date\";s:10:\"2022-10-28\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:259:\"* Tweak - Added additional non validated email user check to sync with LD course access\n* Tweak - Updated display email confirmation message to groups associated courses\n* Fix - Fixed non validated emails getting course access\n* Fix - Fixed PHPDOC block value\";s:4:\"name\";s:42:\"LearnDash Paid Memberships Pro Integration\";s:11:\"description\";s:348:\"PaidMemberships Pro is one of the most popular free membership plugins available for WordPress with robust user statistics and reporting of membership levels. With this integration, you can create membership level access and associate the access levels to LearnDash courses. Customers are auto-enrolled into courses after signing-up for membership.\";s:8:\"category\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"authors\";a:1:{i:0;s:9:\"LearnDash\";}s:17:\"documentation_url\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:58:\"https://www.learndash.com/integrations/paidmembershipspro/\";s:11:\"plugin_file\";s:55:\"learndash-paidmemberships/learndash-paidmemberships.php\";}i:12;a:16:{s:4:\"slug\";s:21:\"learndash-memberpress\";s:4:\"kind\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:12:\"minimum_tier\";s:10:\"essentials\";s:7:\"top_dir\";s:21:\"learndash-memberpress\";s:9:\"main_file\";s:25:\"learndash-memberpress.php\";s:10:\"wporg_slug\";N;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"2.2.2\";s:12:\"release_date\";s:10:\"2022-10-19\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:392:\"* Fix - Updated get live subscription of user rather than cached version.\n* Fix - Updated run expire subscription access in silent queue and update access.\n* Fix - Fixed retroactive tool on multisite installs.\n* Fix - Fixed retroactive tool resetting user access counter on each run.\n* Fix - Fixed error when deactivating plugin.\n* Fix - Fixed unregistered cron events on plugin deactivation.\";s:4:\"name\";s:33:\"LearnDash MemberPress Integration\";s:11:\"description\";s:332:\"MemberPress is a premium WordPress membership plugin that excels in memberships, grouping, coupons, reminders, reports, and more. With this integration you can create membership levels in MemberPress and associate the access levels to LearnDash courses. Customers are then auto-enrolled into courses after signing-up for membership.\";s:8:\"category\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"authors\";a:1:{i:0;s:9:\"LearnDash\";}s:17:\"documentation_url\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:51:\"https://www.learndash.com/integrations/memberpress/\";s:11:\"plugin_file\";s:47:\"learndash-memberpress/learndash-memberpress.php\";}i:13;a:16:{s:4:\"slug\";s:23:\"learndash-gravity-forms\";s:4:\"kind\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:12:\"minimum_tier\";s:10:\"essentials\";s:7:\"top_dir\";s:23:\"learndash-gravity-forms\";s:9:\"main_file\";s:26:\"learndash_gravityforms.php\";s:10:\"wporg_slug\";N;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"2.1.3\";s:12:\"release_date\";s:10:\"2022-10-25\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:641:\"* Fix - Updated improve LD GF select2 box styling.\n* Fix - Updated add horizontal padding to LD option input field.\n* Fix - Updated improve style of LD options select box in GF field choices.\n* Fix - Updated use entry form feed setting to make its filter hook works instead of pulling feed settings from DB.\n* Fix - Fixed editor CSS styles are broken because of jQuery UI base theme CSS.\n* Fix - Fixed undefined array index error.\n* Fix - Fixed incorrect property name is JS script.\n* Fix - Fixed JS conflict error on form edit screen.\n* Fix - Fixed selecting options in LD options select box for GF field choices close GF choices UI flyout.\";s:4:\"name\";s:35:\"LearnDash Gravity Forms Integration\";s:11:\"description\";s:257:\"Gravity Forms is hands-down the industryÔÇÖs best custom form development plugin. With this integration, you can create a completely custom course registration form and associate your online courses to it so that when users register, they are auto-enrolled.\";s:8:\"category\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"authors\";a:1:{i:0;s:9:\"LearnDash\";}s:17:\"documentation_url\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:53:\"https://www.learndash.com/integrations/gravity-forms/\";s:11:\"plugin_file\";s:50:\"learndash-gravity-forms/learndash_gravityforms.php\";}i:14;a:16:{s:4:\"slug\";s:17:\"learndash-bbpress\";s:4:\"kind\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:12:\"minimum_tier\";s:10:\"essentials\";s:7:\"top_dir\";s:17:\"learndash-bbpress\";s:9:\"main_file\";s:21:\"learndash-bbpress.php\";s:10:\"wporg_slug\";N;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"2.2.5\";s:12:\"release_date\";s:10:\"2026-02-25\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:176:\"* Fix - Resolved `_load_textdomain_just_in_time` notice on WordPress 6.7+.\n* Fix - Corrected text domain in dependency check message.\n* Tweak - Added WordPress 6.6 requirement.\";s:4:\"name\";s:29:\"LearnDash bbPress Integration\";s:11:\"description\";s:282:\"bbPress is a forum plugin for WordPress with over 1.5 million downloads. This integration makes it easy for you to add forums to your courses. You can protect the forums so that only users who are enrolled into your courses are able to view content and to post new threads & topics.\";s:8:\"category\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"authors\";a:1:{i:0;s:9:\"LearnDash\";}s:17:\"documentation_url\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:47:\"https://www.learndash.com/integrations/bbpress/\";s:11:\"plugin_file\";s:39:\"learndash-bbpress/learndash-bbpress.php\";}i:15;a:16:{s:4:\"slug\";s:20:\"learndash-thrivecart\";s:4:\"kind\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:12:\"minimum_tier\";s:10:\"essentials\";s:7:\"top_dir\";s:20:\"learndash-thrivecart\";s:9:\"main_file\";s:24:\"learndash-thrivecart.php\";s:10:\"wporg_slug\";N;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.0.3\";s:12:\"release_date\";s:10:\"2024-04-17\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:208:\"* Deprecate - Classes: `LearnDashElementorContainer`, `LearnDashElementorApp`.\n* Tweak - Added compatibility with LearnDash Core v4.13.0.\n* Tweak - Updated functions: `learndash_thrivecart_extra_autoloading`.\";s:4:\"name\";s:32:\"LearnDash ThriveCart Integration\";s:11:\"description\";s:289:\"The LearnDash ThriveCart integration is one of several options for selling your courses. ThriveCart is a premium eCommerce solution that provides several payment options (one-time, subscriptions, trials), advanced analytics, cart abandonment recovery, A/B split testing, upsells, and more.\";s:8:\"category\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"authors\";a:1:{i:0;s:9:\"LearnDash\";}s:17:\"documentation_url\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:50:\"https://www.learndash.com/integrations/thrivecart/\";s:11:\"plugin_file\";s:45:\"learndash-thrivecart/learndash-thrivecart.php\";}i:16;a:16:{s:4:\"slug\";s:17:\"learndash-samcart\";s:4:\"kind\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:12:\"minimum_tier\";s:10:\"essentials\";s:7:\"top_dir\";s:17:\"learndash-samcart\";s:9:\"main_file\";s:21:\"learndash-samcart.php\";s:10:\"wporg_slug\";N;s:7:\"version\";s:7:\"1.1.0.1\";s:12:\"release_date\";s:10:\"2026-01-14\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:61:\"* Security - Tightened security around SamCart notifications.\";s:4:\"name\";s:29:\"LearnDash SamCart Integration\";s:11:\"description\";s:240:\"SamCart is a hosted shopping cart built by marketers, for marketers. It is optimized for conversions so as to increase your total revenue. This integration makes it possible to sell LearnDash courses with this high-converting shopping cart.\";s:8:\"category\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"authors\";a:1:{i:0;s:9:\"LearnDash\";}s:17:\"documentation_url\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:47:\"https://www.learndash.com/integrations/samcart/\";s:11:\"plugin_file\";s:39:\"learndash-samcart/learndash-samcart.php\";}i:17;a:16:{s:4:\"slug\";s:15:\"ld-multilingual\";s:4:\"kind\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:12:\"minimum_tier\";s:10:\"essentials\";s:7:\"top_dir\";s:15:\"ld-multilingual\";s:9:\"main_file\";s:19:\"ld-multilingual.php\";s:10:\"wporg_slug\";N;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.0.0\";s:12:\"release_date\";