gurator module. Easily create unlimited product combinations with layered, attribute-based images and let customers preview their customised product in real time.\n* Feature: Product Gallery: \"Click Anywhere to Open Lightbox\" option.\n* Feature: Product Gallery: Attribute Images for switching gallery images automatically when a customer selects a variation attribute.\n* Feature: Product Gallery: new \"Thumbnails Above Image\", \"3 Column Grid\", \"2 Column Grid Highlighted\", and \"3 Column Grid Highlighted\" layouts.\n* Feature: Quickview: render the full product gallery and support variable products and Show Single Variations.\n* Feature: Sales Booster module for cross-sells and order bumps that increase average order value.\n* Feature: Show Single Variations module for showing product variations as individual products in the shop catalog.\n* Feature: Variation Swatches: accordion mode to collapse attribute swatches and save space on the product page.\n* Feature: Variation Swatches: compatibility with Aelia Currency Switcher, CURCY, WOOCS, WPML/WCML, Easy WooCommerce Discounts, Price Based on Country for WooCommerce, Woo Fees and Discounts, and WooCommerce All Products for Subscriptions.\n* Feature: Variation Swatches: per-attribute and per-term fees with tax handling and a product-edit admin UI.\n* Feature: Variation Swatches: round and square swatch shape, configurable globally or per attribute.\n* Feature: Wishlists module for letting customers save and share their favorite products.\";s:4:\"name\";s:8:\"Shop Kit\";s:11:\"description\";s:99:\"With over 15 powerful modules, Kadence Shop Kit is the most robust WooCommerce extension available.\";s:8:\"category\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"authors\";a:1:{i:0;s:7:\"Kadence\";}s:17:\"documentation_url\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:42:\"https://www.kadencewp.com/kadence-shopkit/\";s:11:\"plugin_file\";s:37:\"kadence-shop-kit/kadence-shop-kit.php\";}i:22;a:16:{s:4:\"slug\";s:20:\"restrict-content-pro\";s:4:\"kind\";s:6:\"plugin\